    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a great car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it\u2019s super reliable and ready for its next adventure. I've taken good care of it, so it's clean and runs smoothly. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
