    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy luster, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is impressively clean and has remained strictly smoke-free; the upholstery is firm and free of tears, while the dashboard and trim remain crack-free. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment screen to the power-adjustable seating, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in great shape: the engine idles quietly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It has been serviced regularly with synthetic oil, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
